Class PropagationTypeAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.checkerframework.framework.type.visitor.AnnotatedTypeScanner<java.lang.Void,​java.lang.Void>

        • org.checkerframework.framework.type.typeannotator.PropagationTypeAnnotator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnotatedTypeVisitor<java.lang.Void,​java.lang.Void>
    public class PropagationTypeAnnotator
extends TypeAnnotator
    PropagationTypeAnnotator adds qualifiers to types where the qualifier to add should be transferred from one or more other types.

    At the moment, the only function PropagationTypeAnnotator provides, is the propagation of generic type parameter annotations to unannotated wildcards with missing bounds annotations.

    See Also:
    PropagationTypeAnnotator traverses trees deeply by default.
